data.text:
​The Mission of the Salamanca IDA is to promote growth in the private sector with employment and investment in the area surrounding and including the City of Salamanca and support the economic and community development of the region.

Eligible projects include: commercial, education/cultural, manufacturing, recreation, research and development, and retail.
